{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Split the child benefit payment if parents share custody",
        "additional_details": "Child benefit for your first child is \u201c\u00a326.05 per week\u201d and \u00a317.25 per additional child. We do not think it is fair that one parent, if they are the one claiming the benefit, can receive the full amount and not be made to share the benefit payment with the other parent who also has custody of the child.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to change child benefits payments so it\u2019s shared between the parents who share 50/50 custody.",
